# Creamy Mashed Potatoes

> #side #vegetarian

- Potatoes | Russet, 3 | Peeled and cubed

Boil potatoes until they are fully cooked.

- Milk | 1 cup  | 
- Butter | 1/2 stick | 
- Garlic | 3 cloves | Lightly smashed
- Thyme | 1 small bunch | 

Heat the garlic, milk, butter, and thyme to just before boiling. Then kill the heat and let it steep for 5 minutes.

Mash potatoes, then strain in milk mixture while hot. Continue to mash until it reaches the desired consistency.

- Salt |  | 
- Black Pepper |  | 

Season with salt and pepper.
